metadata.name: INDIGO I
metadata.description:
"It starts with Me

Interestingly
What am I really?
What am I seeing? What do I believe?
Are we human beings? Am I shaped to be me?
Or a me I hope to be?

It doesnâ€™t matter to us
We are your components, but your thoughts are violent
An impediment to what we are, seriously you leave us mesmerized
This deep ocean you call a heart, so much souls dwell to be blown apart...."
